name: 1 CLEANSE RITUAL
description:
YELLOW-GOLD HEALING LIGHT
DOWNWARD FLOW FROM HEAVENS TO TIPS OF FINGERS AND YOUR HEELS

With divine light
I cleanse myself of all energies
which do not resonate from the love frequency
and the love vibration
or higher, or faster
from all of my bodies
seen and unseen
known and unknown
in all dimensions, realms and worlds
including this one
AND SO IT IS

I send gratitude from the depths of my spirit to [whoever you pray to, your benevolent Ancestors, Spirit, Source, the Universe, your higher self] ✨
